name: Multiplayer Challenge: Boss Deck - Chaos
extDescription:
Multiplayer Challenge Boss Deck – Chaos includes:
• 67 Boss Fight-specific cards
• 33 reprinted cards from previous booster packs, including the Legend rarity cards listed below:
1 Vayne [2-026L]
1 Kuja [6-027L]
1 Sephiroth [7-034L]*
* Sephiroth [7-034L] is a Premium Full Art card, while the others are standard cards.

name: Zalera, the Death Seraph
extDescription: EX BURST Break all the Forwards of costs 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, and 13 opponent controls.

name: Galdes
extDescription:
When Galdes in put from the field into the Break Zone, select up to 3 of the 3 following actions.
"Your opponent randomly discards 1 card from their hand."
"Choose 1 Character other than Card Name Galdes in your Break Zone. Add it to your hand."
"Choose 1 Forward. It loses 10000 power until the end of the turn."

name: Exdeath
extDescription: When Exdeath enters the field, choose up to 3 Forwards among all Break Zones. Play all the Forwards among them of cost equal to or less than the number of Backups you control onto your field.
